{
  "stem": "12053.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After having gone through cancer, she insists she has got a BA.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So, you know, it's something in you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you probably want to prove that you've got something in you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You want to stress the positive side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the fact that so many people lost their parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I always say we 20% who found our parents again-- approximately 15% to 20%-- are tremendously lucky and feel guilty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Most of us do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And to come to terms, for so many children, never have to found their parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Never have grandparents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Their children never had grandparents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When they got married, had children, they hadn't got a mother to turn to, to help with the baby.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It's a dreadful thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And a lot of the people married each other, especially in the hostels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We've got a lot of happy hostel weddings, and we've got a lot of 50th anniversaries coming up just now, the older ones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But it must be stressed that we have many young ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The youngest was four months-- the one I knew personally was four months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Lots of babies of 18 months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There's a wonderful story in the book of two twins being pushed in-- little babies in a-- in a basket being pushed in the train, and how the children looked after them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So, there's some incredible stories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing is now I've sort of woken it's all up again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's still some people who don't want to know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They don't want to be reminded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't fault that, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as we're old and retiring, this is the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somebody said, why didn't you do it 25 years ago?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't the right time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had children to bring up.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
